  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat with a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced onion </strong>with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then<strong> </strong>cook for 5-6 min or until the onion is starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
