    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
