    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, zest <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1700568779234-x200.jpg",
