            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is tender and the stock has absorbed, add your <strong>salmon flakes</strong> and <strong>spinach </strong>to the pan with your <strong>blanched peas</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> and <strong>lemon zest</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a gentle mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1700568788608-x200.jpg",
