            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>salmon, pea & spinach pilaf</strong> topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped herbs</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>lemon yoghurt </strong>and season with a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
